OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FThe family of a man who died from an
OL,8,Faggressive form of cancer has pleaded
OL,9,Fwith health officials to give the
OL,10,Fgreen light to a new treatment, which
OL,11,Foffers hope of a "normal life".
OL,13,FNew father Huw Jones, from
OL,14,FLlanuwchllyn in north Wales, died in
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,17,FHe had been campaigning for
OL,18,Fzanidatamab to be made available for
OL,19,Fall patients with cholangiocarcinoma `
OL,20,Falso known as bile duct cancer.
OL,26,@sD@ROUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FThe NHS's spending watchdog initially
OL,8,Frejected the new targeted treatment
OL,9,Ffor widespread NHS use, in initial
OL,10,Fdraft guidance.
OL,12,FOfficials from Nice are due to meet in
OL,13,FMarch to assess the evidence on the
OL,14,Ftreatment, according to the
OL,15,Fcholangiocarcinoma charity AMMF.
OL,17,FMr Jones, 33, was diagnosed with stage
OL,18,F4 cholangiocarcinoma in 2024 after
OL,19,Fexperiencing a pain in his torso after
OL,20,Ftraining for a triathlon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FHis diagnosis came the day before his
OL,8,Fpregnant partner's 20-week scan for
OL,9,Ftheir first baby.
OL,11,FHe started taking zanidatamab as part
OL,12,Fof a clinical trial in January 2025 `
OL,13,Fthe month his son, Idris, was born.
OL,15,FHis family believe that without
OL,16,Fzanidatamab, they would not have been
OL,17,Fable to spend a year together as a
OL,18,Ffamily of three.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FMr Jones had said: "My condition
OL,8,Fimproved a great deal after I started
OL,9,Fzanidatamab.
OL,11,F"Some of my tumours shrunk in size,
OL,12,Fand I was able to reduce the amount of
OL,13,Fmorphine I was taking for pain relief.
OL,15,F"There are a lot fewer side effects
OL,16,Fcompared to chemotherapy alternatives,
OL,17,FI don't feel as tired and I'm able to
OL,18,Fcontinue doing exercise."
OL,26,@oD@TOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FHe said that the decision to reject
OL,8,Fthe treatment did not make sense to
OL,9,Fhim, as he called on the National
OL,10,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,11,FExcellent (Nice) to revise its
OL,12,Frecommendation.
OL,14,FAfter Mr Jones' death, his partner
OL,15,FCadi Rowlands backed his campaign to
OL,16,Fget the drug approved for NHS use.
OL,18,FAnd his calls were echoed by fellow
OL,19,Fcholangiocarcinoma patient Gareth
OL,20,FHoneybone, from Sheffield.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FMr Honeybone, an NHS surgeon, was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed when he was just 27.
OL,10,FHis tumour was removed through surgery
OL,11,Fand he had a course of chemotherapy
OL,12,Fand was given the all-clear, but a new
OL,13,Ftumour was detected in August 2024.
OL,15,FAfter undergoing chemotherapy and
OL,16,Fimmunotherapy, he started taking
OL,17,Fzanidatamab in January 2025, through a
OL,18,Fclinical trial.
OL,20,FScans have shown that the tumour is no
OL,21,Flonger visible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FMr Honeybone, now 31, said: "I'm one
OL,8,Fof the lucky ones, living a normal
OL,9,Flife again, thanks to zanidatamab.
OL,11,F"I'm back at work full-time ` unlike
OL,12,Fwhen I was having chemo and
OL,13,Fimmunotherapy, when I couldn't work `
OL,14,Fand I was able to visit my brother in
OL,15,FAustralia over Christmas.
OL,26,@oD@]OUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"I'm concerned that not approving this
OL,8,Ftreatment for NHS patients will add to
OL,9,Fthe inequalities in cholangiocarcinoma
OL,10,Fcare we are already seeing ` with
OL,11,Fpeople who are able to access clinical
OL,12,Ftrials or have private healthcare
OL,13,Fbenefiting from new life-extending
OL,14,Ftreatments; and those that can't go on
OL,15,Fa trial or afford to pay for
OL,16,Finsurance, not surviving."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FAMMF said that clinical trial data
OL,8,Fshow that patients treated with
OL,9,Fzanidatamab survived an average of
OL,10,F18.1 months compared with 6.2 months
OL,11,Ffor those receiving current second
OL,12,Fline treatment.
OL,14,FThe treatment, also known as Ziihera,
OL,15,Fis an antibody treatment for patients
OL,16,Fwith a higher-than-normal level of a
OL,17,Fprotein called HER2, which stimulates
OL,18,Ftumours to grow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FIt works by activating the immune
OL,8,Fsystem to remove and kill the cancer
OL,9,Fcells and reduces the levels of HER2
OL,10,Fwhich prevents the cancer from growing.
OL,12,FIt is recommended for use when the
OL,13,Fcancer cannot be removed by surgery,
OL,14,Fhas spread and has previously been
OL,15,Ftreated with at least one other cancer
OL,16,Fmedicine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FPaul Howard, head of policy and
OL,8,Fresearch at AMMF, said: "Whilst we
OL,9,Frecognise that Nice's recommendation
OL,10,Fto reject the use of zanidatamab in
OL,11,Fthe NHS is not final, it is still very
OL,12,Fdisappointing.
OL,14,F"Receiving a diagnosis of
OL,15,Fcholangiocarcinoma is devastating.
OL,17,F"The current treatment options for
OL,18,Fpeople with tumours that have HER2
OL,19,Fgene faults are very limited and often
OL,20,Fcome with significant side effects.
OL,26,@pD@YOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"Zanidatamab has been shown to work
OL,8,Fwell for these patients, offering the
OL,9,Fpossibility not only of longer life,
OL,10,Fbut also to maintain or improve
OL,11,Fquality of life.
OL,13,F"We are hopeful that Nice and the
OL,14,Fpharmaceutical company will be able to
OL,15,Ffind a solution that will enable NHS
OL,16,Fpatients to access this innovative
OL,17,Ftreatment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FA Nice spokesperson said: "We know
OL,8,Fthis provisional decision will be
OL,9,Fdisappointing for people with advanced
OL,10,Fbiliary tract cancer and their
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,F"We understand how important it is to
OL,14,Fhave more treatment options that could
OL,15,Fhelp people live longer and maintain
OL,16,Ftheir quality of life.
OL,18,F"Our independent committee carefully
OL,19,Freviewed all the available evidence.
OL,26,@oD@[OUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"This suggests zanidatamab is likely
OL,8,Fto help people live longer and delay
OL,9,Ftheir cancer getting worse.
OL,11,F"However, the committee was unable to
OL,12,Fmake a positive recommendation based
OL,13,Fon the evidence submitted by the
OL,14,Fcompany at the first meeting.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"There are some important questions
OL,8,Fthat still need answering,
OL,9,Fparticularly around how much extra
OL,10,Fbenefit people would get from taking
OL,11,Fzanidatamab (and) how much it might
OL,12,Fimprove people's quality of life
OL,13,Fcompared to the usual treatments."
OL,15,FThe news comes after an international
OL,16,Fteam of experts called for an urgent
OL,17,Fimprovement in the way patients with
OL,18,Fbile duct cancer are diagnosed and
OL,19,Ftreated.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772758999
OL,3,CBereaved family implores NHS to
OL,4,Capprove new treatment for aggressive
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FA consensus statement published in the
OL,8,Fjournal Nature Reviews
OL,9,FGastroenterology and Hepatology said
OL,10,Foutcomes for people with the cancer
OL,11,Fremain poor.
OL,13,FAbout 3,000 people die from bile duct
OL,14,Fcancer in England each year, making it
OL,15,Fone of the deadliest cancers.
OL,17,FOnly about a quarter of people survive
OL,18,Ffor a year after diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
